== Politics ==
Aalen has arranged a [[municipal association]] with [[Essingen]] and [[Hüttlingen, Baden-Württemberg|Hüttlingen]].

=== Council ===
Since the [[local election]] of 7&nbsp;June&nbsp;2009, the [[municipal council|town council]] consists of 54&nbsp;representatives having a term of five years. The seats are distributed as follows on parties and groups (changes refer to the second last election of 2004):

